value.name: Police: Man shot by officer had rifle, ignored commands
value.description: The Montgomery County Police Department’s statement on an officer’s fatal shooting of 21-year-old Duncan Socrates Lemp contradicts an eyewitness account cited by an attorney for Lemp’s family.
